OL,2,MCardiff Makerspace
OL,4,E-2.377149551379034,52.04057182937612
OL,6,GCardiff Makerspace is a shared
OL,7,Gworkspace in Cardiff for people who
OL,8,Glike to learn and make stuff. A bunch
OL,9,Gof us will be at EMF, so come along
OL,10,Gand say hi to our lovely group of
OL,11,Gpeople! Our members interests include
OL,12,Gelectronics, robotics, woodwork,
OL,13,Gmetalwork, photography, music,
OL,14,Gjewellery making, paper craft and
OL,15,Gtextiles.
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
